EnergyandMineralsMineralResources 
EnergyandMineralsNationalLaboratories";s:4:"link";s:57:"http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/article.asp?ID=4457&from=rss";s:6:"georss";a:2:{s:14:"featuretypetag";s:5:"state";s:11:"featurename";s:3:"NAT";}s:11:"description";s:2659:"
						
						
					
						
						<!--summarystart-->
						<strong>Summary:</strong> The ongoing resource, climate, hazards and environmental issues of the United States are addressed in a new U.S. Geological Survey product, providing an overview of the USGS Mineral Resources Program's multidisciplinary science.
						<hr size="1">
						<!--summaryend-->
		<p><strong>Contact Information:</strong></p>
		<p>
		
					<a href="mailto:hkoontz@usgs.gov">Heidi &nbsp;Koontz </a>
			  			
			
			( Phone: 303-202-4763
		); 
		
		
