USTopo";s:4:"link";s:57:"http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/article.asp?ID=4450&from=rss";s:6:"georss";a:2:{s:14:"featuretypetag";s:5:"state";s:11:"featurename";s:3:"NAT";}s:11:"description";s:7331:"
						
						
					
						
						<!--summarystart-->
						<strong>Summary:</strong> The USGS National Map program is transitioning all of its GIS data download capabilities to its new TNM Download client during the week of February 15, 2016. The new launch page will help users easily find the variety of resources available to get National Map data, download GIS data, visualize and analyze data on the web, or access developer tools such as APIs and map services.
