<tr>
<td><a href="http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/images/2016-02-09/conceptualdiagram.pptx"><img style="width: 220px;" src="http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/images/2016-02-09/pie-chart.png" alt="" /></a></td>
<td><a href="/admin/newsroom/"><img style="width: 330px;" src="http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/images/2016-02-09/fish-importance.jpg" alt="" /></a></td>
</tr>
