<td align="center" valign="top"><a href="http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/images/2016_01_29/ChenegaSummary.jpg"><img src="http://www.usgs.gov/newsroom/images/2016_01_29/ChenegaSummary.jpg" alt="Illustration of sea floor" width="400" /></a></td>
